 U7-e5 tiam3 ti7 hai2-kiN5, chiu7 chhut gun5 cho7 chit8 chiah kiu3-seng chun5 thang ki3-liam7 in e5 chhin-lang5. Hai2-kiN5 e5 siaN5 kap toa7 e5 hiuN-li2 long2 u7 kiu3-seng chun5, ia7 khi2 chit8 keng chhu3 khng3 chun5. Ni5-ni5 u7 ki3 sin-bun5-po3 hou7 lang5 chai tak8 chiah u7 kiu3 kui2 e5 lang5 e5 siN3-mia7, u7 kui2 chap8-e5, kui2 pah-e5 ,kui2 chheng-e5, bo5 tiaN7 tioh8. 
 Ian5-hai2 e5 sou2-chai7 long2 u7 siat lang5, na2 hai2-koan mi5 jit8 tioh8 sun5, iau3-kin2 tak8 mi5 tioh8 kiaN5 ian5-hai2 e5 lou7, khoaN3 tak8 hang7 ho2-se3 a2-bo5. Pun2 siat e5 si5 si7 beh liah8 chau2 se3 e5 lang5, hian7-kim iu5-goan5 tioh8 sun5. Tng kau-chian3 hit si5 in chin-chiaN3 bo5 eng5, taN sui-bong2 peng5-cheng7, tak8 am3 bou2 hiuN-li2 e5 chha5-se3 e5 lang5 tioh8 kiaN5 kui2 phou3-lou7, kau3 tu2-tioh8 pat8 hiuN-li2 e5 chha5-se3 e5 lang5; nng7 lang5 u7 ji7 tioh8 tui3-oaN7 choe3 pin5-ku3 in u7 saN-kiN3, jian5-au7 oat8 tng2-lai5 kau3 pun2 sou2-chai7. 
 Siat-su2 na7 khi2 toa7 hong eng2, chiah-e5 chha5-se3 e5 lang5 tioh8 siong5-se3 khoaN3 hai2-bin7, kiaN-liau2 u7 sim2-mih8 chun5 tu2-tioh8 gui5-hiam2. Na7-si7 u7, in chiu7 po3 ko3 kiu3-seng chun5 e5 lang5. Kiam2-chhai2 chun5 na7 khap8-tioh8 chioh8-thau5, a2-si7 pi7 hong chhe, a2-si7 phoa3-lau7, a2-si7 tu2-tioh8 pat8 hang7 e5 gui5-hiam2, in chiu7 pang3 ho7-phau3 po3 lang5 chai. Khah siong5 si7 mi5-si5; kiam2-chhai2 hiuN-li2 e5 lang5 tang7-bin5 khun3, hut-jian5-kan u7 thiaN-kiN3 ho7-phau3 e5 siaN, ko3 chun5 e5 lang5 chiu7 kin2-kin2 khi2-lai5 chheng7 saN, chau2 khi3 thoa kiu3-seng chun5 pang3 loh8 hai2. 
 U7-si5 pun2 hiuN e5 tho2-hi5 lang5 tu2-tioh8 gui5 hiam2, tioh8 ko3 kiu3-seng chun5 khi3 kiu3 in. Chong2-si7 eng2-si5 thoa chun5, ko3-chun5--e5 chiu7 si7 hiah-e5 tho2-hi5 lang5. In na7 ti7 hai2-bin7 siu7-khou2 chiu7 beh chaiN2-iuN7? Khah beng2 e5 lang5 chiuN7 chun5, kiah8 chiuN2, su7, long5, kang, siong, hu7-jin5-lang5,gin2-na2 long2 ho5-hiap8 thoa chun5 pang3 loh8 hai2. 
 Kiu3-seng chun5 si7 peng3 toa7 chiah, oe7 che7 tit kui2 chap8 lang5. M7 thang siuN toa7 ti3-kau3 boe7 jip8 oeh8 e5 sou2-chai7. Chun5-teng2 u7 khang khak, e7-toe2 chhong3 khah tang7, an2-ni siat-su2 chun5 na7 tu2-tioh8 hong-eng2 chhe to3-peng2, chui2 boe7 jip8 i pak-lai7, chun5 ka-ki7 oe7 koh peng2 chiaN3-bin7 khi2-lai5, boe7 chhin-chhiuN7 peng5-siong5 e5 chun5 to3-peng2 lau5 ti7 chui2-bin7. 
 Chun5 na7 to3-peng2, lang5 kiam2 boe7 tim5-loh8 hai2 mah? Boe7; ko3 kiu3-seng chun5-e5 tak8 lang5 u7 chheng7 chho2 e5 saN, chiu7 oe7 phu5 ti7 chui2-bin7; koh u7 chho2-khoan5 thang hiat hou7 poah8-loh8 hai2 e5 lang5 khiN5, bian2 ti3-kau3 lang5 tim5 si2. 
