 Teng si7 chin toa7 ki, li7 kui2-na7 phou3-lou7, ia7 oe7 khoaN3-kiN3 hit e5 kng, u7 ho7 e5 teng oe7 go5, chit8 bin7 am3, chit8 bin7 kng, u7-e5 poaN3 hun kng, poaN3 hun am3, u7-e5 eng7 u7 sek e5 chhang-kng2, kiam2-chhai2 nng7-e5 peh8, chit8-e5 ang5, chai-iaN2 e5 lang5 chiu7 oe7 hun-piat si7 siok8 tah-loh8 chit8 cho7 teng-thah. 
