 Lun7 chhiu7-na5, Ngou5-kok, Bi2-kok, A-hui-Li7-ka u7 chin toa7-e5, lai7-tiong hiah-e5 chhiu7 ka-ki7 lak chi2, ka-ki7 chhut, hoat kau3 chin toa7 chang5, long2 m7 bian2 lang5 kou3. Bat khoaN3-tioh8 tou5 kong2, u7 chit8 chang5 chhiu7 tioh8 20 lang5 khan lai5 ui5 i e5 chhiu7 thau5, chiah oe7 thang lam2 ke3, kho2-kian3 si7 cham2-jian5 toa7. Chong2-si7 toa7 chang5 chhiu7 bo5 tek-khak long2 u7 toa7 lou7-eng7, chhin-chhiuN7 oa2 Ka-gi7 A-li2-san soaN u7 hoat chin toa7 chang5, m7-ku2 u7-e5 lai7-bin7 noa7 khi3. Ia7 m7-si7 long2-chong2 bo5 lou7-eng7, u7-e5 thang cho7 choa2, choe3 pou3, choe3 chheng3-ioh8, i2-kip8 pat8 mih8 e5 lou7-eng7, m7-bian2 chit8 sut-a2 phah-sng2. Hit ho7 na7 teh chho3 si7 chin gui5-hiam2, ai3 hai7-tioh8 chho3-chhiu7 lang5 e5 siN3-mia7. Hit ho7 toa7 e5 chhiu7-na5 chin am7, ia7 chin ou-am3, u7 sai, u7 hou2, pa3, chhai5-long5 kap chin choe7 khoan2 e5 ia2-siu3 i2-kip8 tok8-choa5. 
 Ke2-chi2 chhiu7 u7 chin choe7 khoan2. Tak8 kok long2 u7 in e5 ke2-chi2, ia7 long2 oe7 iuN2-chhi7 lang5 e5 seng-khu. Koh chhiu7 oe7 im3-ng2, hou7 lang5 khah boe7 joah8, kiaN5 lou7 e5 lang5 chiu7 chai i e5 toa7 li7-ek. Kai-chai3 hian7-si5 pou-thau5 e5 toa7 lou7 long2 u7 chai-cheng3, hou7 chhut-goa7 lang5 chhut-jip8 chin li7-pian7. Chhiu7-na5 chin choe7 na7 loh8-hou7 chiu7 oe7 hou7 thiN-khi3 khah liang5, lang5 chiu7 khah song2-khoai3. Ti7 Ngou5-kok khah u7 bou7-seng7 e5 chhiu7-na5. 
 U7 chhiu7 bo5 kiat ke2-chi2, chong2-si7 u7 pat8 mih8 hou7 lang5 tit-tioh8 chin choe7 chiN5. Chhin-chhiuN7 Tai5-oan5 soaN-lai7 e5 chiuN-lo2 sou2 boe7 chhut, siu-jip8 e5 chiN5 m7-si7 sio2-khoa2, bo5 khah su kiat ke2-chi2 e5 chhiu7. Koh chin choe7 lang5 u7 kang thang choe3. Teh kek chiuN-lo2 e5 si5, u7 lang5 tioh8 chho3-chhiu7 hiaN5 he2, ia7 u7-e5 tioh8 khi3 thoaN2 lo2-phi2, koh u7-e5 tioh8 kek chiuN-lo2 kap iu5. ChiuN-lo2 chin choe7 hang7 ho2 eng7, oe7 choe3 ioh8, boah seng-khu, ia7 thang tu5-khi3 chiu3-thang5, chian2-a2,bian2-tit i-chiuN5 siu7 sun2-hai7. 
