 10. Ai-kip8 
 I 
 Tng Ku7-iok e5 si5-tai7 Hi-pek-lai5 chok8 kap saN e5 te3-kok put-chi2 u7 kan-siap8, u7-si5 li7-ek u7-si5 sun2-hai7, chiu7-si7 Pa-pi2-lun5, A-sut8 kap Ai-kip8, ki5-tiong lun7 in e5 seng-hoat8 kap chong-kau3, te7-it iau3-kin2 si7 Ai-kip8. Tu2-tioh8 ki-hng hit si5 in e5 chou2-kong loh8-khi3 Ai-kip8; ti7 Ai-kip8 Iok-sek kap Mou5-se i2-kip8 in e5 peh-seN3 siu7 kau3-lian7 soa3 chiam7-si5 hou7 in po2-hou7. 
 Ti7 au7-tai7 Ai-kip8 tauh8-tauh8 teh chhap I2-sek-liat8 e5 su7, khah siong5 bo5 li7-ek. U7-si5 choe3 tui3-tek8, u7-si5 koe2-choe3 peng5-iu2, ki5-sit8 beh ti2-tng A-sut8, chiu7-si7 tang-pak u7 koan5-se3 e5 kok. A-sut8 e5 jin5-sin5 Liap8-sa-ki kong2, "Li2 oa2-kho3 Ai-kip8 mah? Kiam2 m7 chai i si7 chhin-chhiuN7 i2-keng chih8 e5 lou7-tek, lang5 hoaN7 i, tek-khak chhi3-chhak8 i e5 chhiu2" (2 Ong5 18 : 2). Chit e5 oe7 si7 tui3-tek8 kong2-e5, iau2-ku2 si7 sit8, Ai-kip8 khah siong5 si7 boe7 kho3-tit. 
 Toa7-soe3. Ai-kip8 e5 thou2 toe7 kap Ka-lam5--e5 toa7 koh-iuN7. Ka-lam5 si7 soaN-toe7, Ai-kip8 si7 piN5-iuN5. Ka-lam5 choe7-choe7 sou2-chai7 san2-san2, Ai-kip8 hui-siong5 pui5. Ka-lam5 soe3, Ai-kip8 chin tng5 chong2-si7 oeh8-oeh8, tui3 lam5 kau3 pak Ni5-lo5 ho5 oat8-lai5 oat8-khi3 ti7 tiong-ng. 
 Ai-kip8 e5 khi3-hau7 siang7 ho2. U7-si5 ti7 ho5-piN oe7 joah8, chong2-si7 khong-khi3 siong5-siong5 chin chheng. Han2-tit loh8 hou7. 
 Ni5-lo5 ho5. Ai-kip8 kok ki5-sit8 si7 tui3 Ni5-lo5 ho5 chiah u7. Ni5-lo5 ho5 u7 nng7 e5 goan5-thau5, ti7 lam5-si3 kap ti7 tang-lam5-si3 kai3 hng7 e5 koaiN5 soaN. Ti7-hia chhun-thiN si5 loh8 toa7 hou7, koh u7 iuN5 soaN teng2 e5 seh, tui3 an2-ni Ni5-lo5 ho5 chiu7 tiong3 toa7 chui2. Kau3 6 geh8 kan u7 tiong3 chui2 ti7 Ai-kip8 e5 kiaN-siaN5(Cairo); kau3 hit si5 ho5 e5 siang peng5-piN moa2-si3-koe3 si7 chui2, ti3-kau3 chin choe7 hiuN-sia7 na2 hai2-su7. Sou2 chhiang5-loh8-lai5 e5 ho2 thou5 chiu7 che7-toe2, kau3 chui2 the3 hiah-e5 hng5 long2 u7 chit8 ian5 e5 pui5-thou5 ti7 teng2-bin7, tak8 ni5 si7 an2-ni. U7-si5 chit8 ni5 kan u7 siu lak8 tang. Chiau3 an2-ni khoaN3 Ai-kip8 u7 hiah choe7 ngou2-kok, long2 si7 ui7-tioh8 Ni5-lo5 ho5 sou2 chhiang5-loh8-lai5 e5 ho2 thou5. Na7 m7 si7 chit tiau5 ho5 chiu7 Ai-kip8 oe7 choe3 khong3 ia2 chhin-chhiuN7 A-lat-pek hit khoan2. 
 Seng3-chheh tauh8-tauh8 ki3 Ai-kip8 e5 pui5. Si7 in-ui7 an2-ni Nga2-kok e5 kiaN2 khi3 hia. Ti7 Chhong3-se3-ki3 ia7 u7 kong2 ti7 Sou2-to-ma2 hia "thou2-toe7 long2-chong2 lun7-tek8, chhin-chhiuN7 Ia5-ho5-hoa e5 hng5 thang kap Ai-kip8 saN pi2-pheng7." I2-sek-liat8 peh-seN3 ti7 khong3-ia2 ia7 siau3-liam7 Ai-kip8 e5 chhai3-soe chin chhiong-seng7. 
 Po2-lo5 khi3 I-tai7-li7 e5 si5, u7 tah "A-lek8-san-tai7 e5 chun5" (Heng7 27:6). A-lek8-san-tai7 si7 ti7 Ai-kip8 e5 pak-si3, tui3 hia siong-chun5 chai3 ngou2-kok kau3 Lo5-ma2. 
 Choh hng5 e5 hoat-tou7 : Sui-jian5 tit-tioh8 ho5 e5 li7-ek, iau2-ku2 Ai-kip8 lang5 boe7 eng7-tit pin5-toaN7. Tioh8 khui chun3-kau khan chui2 kau3 in e5 hng5. U7 eng7 tiau3-o kap chui2-chhia; u7 chit8 khoan2 e5 chhia lioh8-a2 chhin-chhiuN7 Tai5-oan5 A-kau5 thiaN hit ho7 chui2-la5-gia5. Chong2-si7 tioh8 eng7 gu5 e5 lat8 kap lang5 e5 kang, in-ui7 toe7-bin7 hiah-nih8 piN5 chun3-kau e5 chui2 boe7-oe7 ka-ki7 lau5. 
