 Ai-kip8 chit si5 teh heng, cheng3-su7 khah ho2, lang5-giah8 khah choe7. Koh si7 tu2 ti7 A-hui-li7-ka, A-se-a kap Au-chiu sio-chiap e5 sou2-chai7. sou2-i2 chin lau7-jiat8. Ng3-bang7 ti7-hia e5 soan-kau3-su sou2 choe3 e5 kang tit-tioh8 Chu2 toa7 si-un, thang chiaN5 sian-ti sou2 ki3: "Ia5-ho5-hoa tek-khak kau3-hun3 Ai-kip8 lang5 hou7 in bat I... Hiah-e5 Ai-kip8 lang5 Ia5-ho5-hoa khi2-thau5 kang3 chai-e7; lou7-be2 kiu3 in. Ai-kip8 lang5 si7 Goa2 keng2-soan2--e5 " (Sai3 19:21,22,25). 
